quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  15,71,"(Lot) said: “These (the girls of the nation) are my daughters (to marry lawfully), if you must act.”"
  15,72,"Truly, by your life (O Muhammad), they were wandering blindly in their wild intoxication"
  15,73,So the awful blast overtook them at the time of sunrise
  15,74,And We turned it (towns of Sodom in Palestine) upside down and rained to them stones of baked clay
  15,75,Surely! In this are signs for those who see
  15,76,"And surely, they (the cities) are on an established road (from Makkah to Syria i.e. the place where the Dead Sea is now)"
  15,77,Surely! Therein is indeed a sign for the believers
  15,78,"And surely, the people in the wood (the people of Midian to whom Prophet Shuaib was sent by Allah) were also wrongdoers"
  15,79,"So, We took vengeance on them. They are both (ruined) on a clear road"
  15,80,"And surely, the people of Hijr (the rocky tract) denied the Messengers"
  15,81,"And We gave them Our Verses, but they were averse to them"
  15,82,And they used to cut out secure homes in the mountains
  15,83,But the awful blast overtook them in the early morning
  15,84,and all their earnings (building homes by craving the rock) did not avail
  15,85,"And We have not created the heavens, the earth, and all that is between them except with truth. Surely, the Hour (of Doom) is coming, so overlook (O Muhammad) their faults with gracious forgiveness"
  15,86,"Surely, your Lord is the All-Knowing Creator"
  15,87,"And indeed, We have given you 7 of the repeatedly recited Verses (Al-Fatihah) and the Glorious Qur’an"
  15,88,"Don’t look with your eyes at what We have bestowed on certain classes of them (disbelievers), nor grieve over them. And lower your wings (be courteous) to the believers"
  15,89,"And say (O Muhammad): “I am indeed the plain Warner.”"
  15,90,As We have sent down (this warning) on the dividers